      "content": "## CHAPTER 7 SEASON 3\n- What are surge maps?\n - - A surge map is a map with the best locations for surge bases.\n - - Surge bases are the best locations from which you have the best visibility on other teams and you can base up at these locations and look for surge tags.\n\nFor more information about surge:\n⁠\uD83C\uDF29️・https://discord.com/channels/971731167621574666/1126853717333917718\n⁠\uD83C\uDF29️・https://discord.com/channels/971731167621574666/997469360518082601\n\n\uD83D\uDFE2 / \uD83D\uDFE9 = Good\n\uD83D\uDD35 / \uD83D\uDFE6 = Medium\n\uD83D\uDFE5 = Bad\n\n-# Credits to @Fantastic for doing the map",
